@version("1.0.0")
package design

// `middlewares` declares ProfileAuth + RequestStamp in a separate
// folder; a `middleware` declaration in one folder is visible to
// `@middlewares(...)` decorators in another.
// `profile-service` holds ProfileService split across multiple files
// (primary + two `extend service` blocks), one folder per service.
// `admin` holds AdminService — a separate service in its own folder.
// `xshared` + `xrefs` form the cross-package reference matrix fixture:
// every shape a `xshared.X` qualified ref can take is exercised in
// xrefs, covering cross-package resolution across validate / transport
// / openapi.
